15 September 2008The Directors-General (DGs) of the Social Cluster will brief the media on progress made with regards to the cluster s contribution to the Programme of Action (POA).The briefing, the second of the year by the DGs, will provide an in-depth report on the work of the cluster.The briefing will take place as follows:Date: 17 September 2008 (Wednesday) Time: 13h00 Venue: Union Buildings, Room 153, PretoriaNB: There will be a link up to the Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town.Enquiries Bongani Mlangeni (Pretoria) Cell: 073 525 3107Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)